---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Facilitator pathway"
  description="Teach Camp Claude yourself. A licensable curriculum and shared brand for trainers, consultants, and educators bringing AI fluency to their audiences."
  activeNav="facilitate"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Facilitator pathway</div>
    <h1>Teach Camp Claude <em>yourself</em>.</h1>
    <p class="dek">The open curriculum isn't a loss leader. It's the training ground. Study the material, complete a train-the-trainer, and run your own Camp Claude cohorts under a shared brand.</p>
    <div class="meta">
      <span>Opens Q3 2026</span><span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>First cohort: 8–10 seats</span><span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>Application required</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip ink">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Why this exists</div>
      <div class="argument">
        <p>AI fluency training is a <strong>ten-figure category</strong> that doesn't have a standard curriculum yet. Every corporate trainer, consultant, and community educator is writing their own — badly, from scratch, every time.</p>
        <p>Brandon can run maybe <strong>six cohorts a year</strong>. The answer isn't to teach harder — it's to <em>license the curriculum</em> and train other facilitators to deliver it under a shared brand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip cream">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The pathway</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Four steps from <em>reader</em> to <em>certified facilitator</em>.</h2>

      <div class="pathway">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">01</div>
          <div><h4>Study the <em>open curriculum</em></h4><span class="duration">~ 4 weeks self-paced</span></div>
          <p>Read every article on the <a href="/learn">Learn</a> page. Complete the automation equation worksheet. Understand the governance pattern.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">02</div>
          <div><h4>Attend a <em>Foundations cohort</em></h4><span class="duration">4 live sessions · $299</span></div>
          <p>Experience the curriculum from the learner's seat. You can't teach what you haven't lived.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">03</div>
          <div><h4>Complete <em>train-the-trainer</em></h4><span class="duration">2-day intensive + 30-day mentorship</span></div>
          <p>Two days of facilitator training — how each session lands, failure modes, intervention points. Plus 30 days mentorship with observation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">04</div>
          <div><h4>Run your <em>first cohort</em></h4><span class="duration">Shadow-co-facilitated · then solo</span></div>
          <p>First cohort is co-facilitated with Brandon observing. Second cohort is solo. Full rev share from cohort one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip cream" id="licensing">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Licensing</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">The curriculum is <em>free to learn from</em>. Teaching it commercially requires a license.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead" style="text-align:left; margin-left:0;">
        Camp Claude curriculum is published under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/">CC BY-NC 4.0</a>.
        Anyone can read it, share it, remix it, and teach it in non-commercial settings — free community workshops,
        student groups, personal study — with attribution.
      </p>
      <p class="section-lead" style="text-align:left; margin-left:0;">
        <strong>Commercial teaching — paid cohorts, corporate training, licensing to an employer, certification
        programs — requires a commercial license.</strong> The facilitator pathway above is the primary route;
        direct licensing is available for organizations training at scale internally.
      </p>
      <p class="section-lead" style="text-align:left; margin-left:0;">
        Licensing inquiries: <a href="mailto:facilitators@campclaude.ai">facilitators@campclaude.ai</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip" id="waitlist">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Join the waitlist</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2 center">Eight to ten seats. <em>Tell us who you are</em>.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead center">Applications open Q2 2026. We're selecting for curriculum fit, audience reach, and a track record of quality training.</p>

      <form class="waitlist" action="#" method="post">
        <label><span class="field-label">Your name</span><input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="e.g. Alex Martinez" /></label>
        <label><span class="field-label">Email</span><input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@work.com" /></label>
        <label><span class="field-label">Role / organization</span><input type="text" name="role" required placeholder="e.g. Senior L&amp;D at Acme, or independent consultant" /></label>
        <label>
          <span class="field-label">Which persona best fits you?</span>
          <select name="persona" required>
            <option value="">Select one…</option>
            <option>Corporate trainer / L&amp;D leader</option>
            <option>Community organizer / educator</option>
            <option>Independent consultant</option>
            <option>University / professional school</option>
            <option>Other</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label><span class="field-label">Who's your audience?</span><textarea name="audience" placeholder="A few sentences on the people you'd run cohorts for."></textarea></label>
        <label><span class="field-label">Relevant training experience</span><textarea name="experience" placeholder="What have you taught or facilitated before?"></textarea></label>
        <button type="submit">Join the waitlist</button>
        <p class="small">No spam. You'll hear from us when applications open. Camp Claude is a RUDI program, not affiliated with Anthropic.</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 48px 72px; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 92px; line-height: 0.96; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 28px; max-width: 14ch; text-wrap: balance; }
  h1 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .dek { font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 40px; max-width: 48ch; }
  .meta { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding-top: 28px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); max-width: 700px; }
  .meta span { margin-right: 28px; }
  .meta .dot { color: var(--rust); margin: 0 12px; }

  .strip { padding: 88px 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .strip .inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .strip.cream { background: var(--cream); }
  .strip.ink { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border-top: none; }
  .section-eyebrow { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .strip.ink .section-eyebrow { color: var(--rust-soft); }
  .section-h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 32px; text-wrap: balance; }
  .section-h2.center { text-align: center; }
  .section-h2 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .section-lead { max-width: 60ch; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 auto 48px; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; }

  .argument { max-width: 900px; font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.35; color: rgba(244,238,227,0.85); text-wrap: pretty; }
  .argument p { margin: 0 0 24px; }
  .argument p strong { color: var(--paper); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; }

  .pathway { margin-top: 48px; }
  .step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 48px; padding: 36px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); align-items: baseline; }
  .step:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .step .num { font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 72px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: var(--rust); }
  .step h4 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .step h4 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .step .duration { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
  .step p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0; max-width: 58ch; }

  .waitlist { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--paper); padding: 48px; border-radius: 3px; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .waitlist label { display: block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .waitlist .field-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; display: block; }
  .waitlist input, .waitlist textarea, .waitlist select { width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 2px; background: var(--paper-soft); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); }
  .waitlist textarea { min-height: 90px; resize: vertical; }
  .waitlist button { display: block; width: 100%; background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); padding: 16px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 2px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 8px; }
  .waitlist button:hover { background: var(--rust); }
  .waitlist .small { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 16px 0 0; text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hero { padding: 48px 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 48px; }
    .dek { font-size: 22px; }
    .section-h2 { font-size: 36px; }
    .argument { font-size: 22px; }
    .step { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .step .num { font-size: 52px; }
    .waitlist { padding: 28px; }
    .strip { padding: 48px 24px; }
  }
</style>
